cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR 

This paper deals with object detection in specific scenes, which is a common problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new formalism for transfer learning, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper uses spatio-temporal information and confidence scores, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper deals with traffic datasets, which could be related to computer security (cs.CR).
